description:
Atticus reached out to us a few weeks ago and said he was really excited to be a part of SeanCody, so we decided we would throw him in the deep end. Once he got here, Atticus walked around the studio in awe.
 
“I’ve been a fan of the site pretty much my whole life, so this is like a dream come true.” He said with a huge smile on his face. 

Atticus also admitted that he had a bit of a crush on Rowan. 
“What is about him that turns you on?”
“I don't know. I think we have the same sense of humor and personality. Also, I think he's really cute.”

Since Atticus was brand new, Rowan actually took him under his wing and they hung out before the shoot.

“What did you guys do?” I had to ask

Atticus got all bashful. “It was kinda like a date. We went to the movies and out to grab some food.”

Rowan started to laugh. “I guess it was a date when you say it like that!”

Once they got to fucking you could tell the Atticus was really getting into it. I pulled him aside to check in with him. He was smiling from ear to ear. 

“This is the best day of my life!”
title: Newcomer Atticus & Rowan: Bareback
